k and I have to restart the game.- level of detail in mission control room was probably designed with ZX Spectrum in mindThis is not to say that the game is worthless, there are several aspects that are pretty good:- technology tree is rather short, but organized in sensible way- Mars shown as far, lifeless, desolate place.Long story short, currently the game is piece of you-know-what, but in few months it may become something worthwhile. Meanwhile, I'm getting back to absolutely fantastic Kerbal Space Program!"
