d potential, which I am excited to see released. there will be patches along the way and many MANY additions but I look forward to every single one of them. Sure it's rough around the edges, and I probably sound extremely forgiving for this game, but it's because I can see it will be amazing and fun.Small area to target but you hit the nail on the head! Absolutely amazing work guys! I look forward to the future of this!"
